'''貓肉'''是以[[猫|猫]]为原料的肉食。人类在史前时代就有食用猫肉的记录，<ref name="TaylorNegus1989">{{cite book|author1=David Taylor|author2=Daphne Negus|author3=Dave King |author4=Jane Burton |title=The Ultimate Cat Book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rPdFgZzns30C&pg=PA9&dq=northern+italy+eat+cats&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwik2qSL88LPAhXGGh4KHYk9ApkQ6AEIQjAH#v=onepage&q=northern%20italy%20eat%20cats&f=false|year=1989|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=978-0-671-68649-9|pages=9|language=en}}</ref>雖然貓是寵物，而部分国家至今仍有食用猫肉的传统，這是不違法的（只要不是偷竊他人家貓或食用保育類品種等）。中国古籍《[[本草纲目|本草纲目]]》记载猫肉味道不佳，不适合食用，故当时极少有人食用<ref>《本草纲目》：然狸肉入食，猫肉不佳，亦不入食品，故用之者稀</ref>。
== 各地食用情况 ==
=== 亚洲 ===
在中国廣東，貓肉是傳統菜[[龍虎鳳|龍虎鳳]]的原料之一，当地人认为它能补身子。猫大腿的肉会制成肉丸煲汤，肠胃也会食用，頭部和其餘部分则会被丟棄。现在只有极其少数的中国人会食用猫肉，绝大部分人则将猫作为宠物饲养。[[深圳市|深圳市]]和[[珠海市|珠海市]]已于2020年禁止食用猫肉<ref>{{Cite web|title=深圳珠海相继禁食猫狗肉 律师：动物保护上了一个新台阶|url=https://finance.sina.cn/china/gncj/2020-04-16/detail-iirczymi6658787.d.html|accessdate=2020-08-16|date=2020-04-16|last=sina_mobile|work=finance.sina.cn}}</ref>。

在日本，直到[[江户时代|江户时代]]末一直有食用猫肉的记录。<ref name="hanleycat66">{{Cite book |last=Hanley |first=Susan |title=Everyday Things in Premodern Japan |year=1997 |page=66 |language=en}}</ref>在[[琉球群島|琉球群島]]，猫肉是用于治疗[[胸膜炎|胸膜炎]]、[[气管炎|气管炎]]、[[肺病|肺病]]和[[痔瘡|痔瘡]]的传统食物。<ref>{{cite book|author1=渡口初美|title=沖縄の食養生料理|year=1979|location=国際料理学院|pages=12|language=ja}}</ref>

食用貓肉在[[朝鲜半岛|朝鲜半岛]]是神經痛和[[關節炎|關節炎]]的民間療法，而当地現代消費者也青睐喝貓肉湯。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://saynotodogmeat.net/2014/02/19/boiled-alive-cat-meat-soup-south-korea/ |title=Boiled Alive Cat Meat Soup, South Korea |work=SAY NO TO DOG MEAT.NET |accessdate=2015-11-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123001003/http://saynotodogmeat.net/2014/02/19/boiled-alive-cat-meat-soup-south-korea/ |archivedate=2015-11-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://our-compass.org/2012/04/09/ban-south-korean-dog-and-cat-meat-trade/|title=Ban South Korean dog and cat meat trade|work=Our Compass|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117071121/https://our-compass.org/2012/04/09/ban-south-korean-dog-and-cat-meat-trade/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animalliberationfront.com/ALFront/Actions-Korea/KoreaDogMeatUpdate.htm|title=Important Update On South Korean Dog And Cat Meat Trade|publisher=|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822214541/http://www.animalliberationfront.com/ALFront/Actions-Korea/KoreaDogMeatUpdate.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://koreandogs.org/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023065537/http://koreandogs.org/ |archivedate=2015-10-23 |df= }}</ref>

在越南，食用猫肉属非法行为，但民众仍有食用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailymeal.com/9-countries-eat-cats-and-dogs-slideshow|title=9 Countries That Eat Cats and Dogs (Slideshow)|work=The Daily Meal|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123031907/http://www.thedailymeal.com/9-countries-eat-cats-and-dogs-slideshow|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailymeal.com/9-countries-eat-cats-and-dogs/11414|title=9 Countries That Eat Cats and Dogs|work=The Daily Meal|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123030849/http://www.thedailymeal.com/9-countries-eat-cats-and-dogs/11414|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://vietnamcoracle.com/cat-meat/|title=Cat Meat|work=Vietnam Coracle|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123042103/http://vietnamcoracle.com/cat-meat/|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedropoutdiaries.com/2012/11/the-truth-about-cats-dogs-in-vietnam/|title=The Truth About Cats & Dogs In Vietnam - The Dropout Diaries|work=The Dropout Diaries|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123033439/http://www.thedropoutdiaries.com/2012/11/the-truth-about-cats-dogs-in-vietnam/|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/travel/international/5337677/Where-cat-sits-happily-on-the-menu|title=Where cat sits happily on the menu|work=Stuff|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413153304/http://www.stuff.co.nz/travel/5337677/Where-cat-sits-happily-on-the-menu|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Global-News/2010/0722/Why-do-Vietnamese-keep-cats-on-a-leash-Hint-What-s-for-dinner|title=Why do Vietnamese keep cats on a leash? (Hint: What's for dinner?)|author=The Christian Science Monitor|work=The Christian Science Monitor|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024033440/https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Global-News/2010/0722/Why-do-Vietnamese-keep-cats-on-a-leash-Hint-What-s-for-dinner|dead-url=no}}</ref>当地貓肉市場需求较大，河內的貓通常由中國和寮國偷運入境。据统计，越南每年要食用超过400万只猫。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://new.qq.com/omn/20200727/20200727A0OWQI00.html/|title=每年要吃掉400万只猫！？这个国家的人是疯了么？|work=[腾讯新闻]|accessdate=2020-11-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150417/594681/|title=越南恐怖「貓餐廳」　一天吃掉30隻貓|work=[[苹果日报_(台湾)|苹果日报]]|accessdate=2017-02-08}}</ref>贩卖猫肉的餐厅通常以“[[wiktionary:tiểu_hổ|tiểu hổ]]”（意为“小虎”）代指猫肉。<ref name="Hopkins2004">{{cite book|author=Jerry Hopkins|title=Extreme Cuisine: The Weird and Wonderful Foods That People Eat|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4ZPTAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA25&dq=northern+italy+eat+cats&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwik2qSL88LPAhXGGh4KHYk9ApkQ6AEIIjAB#v=onepage&q=northern%20italy%20eat%20cats&f=false|date=2004-05-15|publisher=Tuttle Publishing|isbn=978-1-4629-0472-3|pages=25–}}</ref><ref name="Hopkins2014"/>

印度的部分地区也有食用猫肉的习惯。猫肉是Narikurvar族人婚礼的菜肴之一。在男性婴儿出生时，Narikurvar族人有时也会烹饪猫肉汤庆祝。<ref name="huffindia">{{cite news|publisher=HuffingtonPost|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.in/2016/11/01/for-biryani-in-chennai-cats-are-being-boiled-alive/?ncid=fcbklnkinhpmg00000001|title=For biryani in Chennai, cats are being boiled alive, sold for Rs 100 per kg|accessdate=2017-02-08|date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104041009/http://www.huffingtonpost.in/2016/11/01/for-biryani-in-chennai-cats-are-being-boiled-alive/?ncid=fcbklnkinhpmg00000001|archive-date=2016-11-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 其它地区 ===
十八世纪的英国曾有食用猫肉的记录。<ref name="The Cat Eaters">{{cite web |url=http://www.forteantimes.com/features/articles/260/the_cat_eaters.html |accessdate=2009-10-12 |title=The Cat Eaters |publisher=forteantimes.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090521072202/http://www.forteantimes.com/features/articles/260/the_cat_eaters.html |archivedate=2009-05-21 |df= }}</ref>
西班牙和法国的部分地区有食用猫肉的习惯。<ref name="Albala2003"/>意大利北部也存在食用猫肉的现象，<ref name="Hopkins2004"/><ref name="Hopkins2014">{{cite book|author=Jerry Hopkins|title=Strange Foods|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WXtzBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA8&dq=northern+italy+eat+cats&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwik2qSL88LPAhXGGh4KHYk9ApkQ6AEIHDAA#v=onepage&q=northern%20italy%20eat%20cats&f=false|date=2014-12-23|publisher=Tuttle Publishing|isbn=978-1-4629-1676-4|pages=8–}}</ref>人们至今仍对该国北部的[[维琴察|维琴察]]人吃猫肉存有[[刻板印象|刻板印象]]。<ref name="Albala2003">{{cite book|author=Ken Albala|title=Food in Early Modern Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4f-l3-KG0LcC&pg=PA66&dq=northern+italy+eat+cats&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwik2qSL88LPAhXGGh4KHYk9ApkQ6AEIMTAE#v=onepage&q=northern%20italy%20eat%20cats&f=false|year=2003|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-313-31962-4|pages=66–}}</ref>

在秘鲁，猫肉不是常见菜肴，但在[[上欽查|上欽查]]和[[瓦里_(秘魯)|瓦里]]，猫肉是传统菜肴[[fricassee|fricassee]]的原料之一。<ref name="FEATURE - 'Cat-eaters' take note - feline feast at Peru festival">{{cite web| url = http://www.planetark.com/dailynewsstory.cfm/newsid/12575/newsDate/28-Sep-2001/story.htm| accessdate = 2008-02-16| title = 'Cat-eaters' take note - feline feast at Peru festival| publisher = planetark.com| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040911063224/http://www.planetark.com/dailynewsstory.cfm/newsid/12575/newsDate/28-Sep-2001/story.htm| archive-date = 2004-09-11| dead-url = yes}}</ref>
在澳大利亚[[愛麗斯泉|愛麗斯泉]]地区，当地[[澳大利亚原住民|原住民]]有烧烤野猫肉的传统，他们甚至发明了炖猫肉的食谱。而后来，当地的一些非原住民也开始食用猫肉。<ref name="Australia">{{Cite news|url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/6974687.stm|publisher= BBC News|title= Australians cook up wild cat stew|date= 2007-09-02|accessdate= 2017-02-08|first= Phil|last= Mercer|archive-date= 2021-02-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210226151024/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/6974687.stm|dead-url= no}}</ref>在喀麥隆，当地的一些文化认为，食用猫肉会给人们帶來好運。<ref>{{Cite news|url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/2857891.stm|title= The cat eaters of Cameroon|publisher= BBC News|date= 2003-03-17|accessdate= 2017-02-08|first= Francis|last= Ngwa-Niba|archive-date= 2020-04-12|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200412151528/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/2857891.stm|dead-url= no}}</ref>

